39:10.682 --> 39:13.048
Yeah, you're, uh——
You're a simple kid, Epstein.

39:13.101 --> 39:16.013
A little doubting Thomas in your ear,
and you're gold. Thank you.

39:16.062 --> 39:17.051
(pats back)

39:18.940 --> 39:20.146
How'd you do it?

39:20.191 --> 39:21.806
