39:21.860 --> 39:24.943
got him to trust me, and then,
when he wasn't paying attention,

39:24.988 --> 39:26.853
l stabbed him in the back.

39:28.324 --> 39:30.155
Turns out I'm pretty good at it.

39:39.669 --> 39:41.910
Chris.

39:41.963 --> 39:44.921
Can I, uh——
Can I go home with you now?

39:49.053 --> 39:50.042
No.

39:50.096 --> 39:51.461
Come on.

39:51.514 --> 39:55.052
