not here to arrest me,

40:40.146 --> 40:41.352
'cause I'm a little busy right now.

40:41.397 --> 40:44.104
No,no,no.
No, uh, it's this kid.

40:44.150 --> 40:45.811
Uh...

40:45.860 --> 40:48.101
I know this kid who might be
in a bit of trouble.

40:48.154 --> 40:49.985
I want to find some way
to help keep him

40:50.031 --> 40:51.567
on the straight and narrow, and...

40:51.616 --> 40:55.108
l was kind of hoping, if maybe he did
some volunteer work for your project,

40:55.161 --> 40:57.277
the prosecutor might be more lenient.

40:57.330 --> 40:59.571
Well, you know, I can always
use a helping hand.

40:59.624 --> 41:04.334
Good. Great. Thank you.

41:05.380 --> 41:06.415
You know, it takes a brave man

41:06.464 --> 41:08.375
to hang on to hope
in this day and age.

41:11.511 --> 41:15.174
Uh, you mind if I stick around
for a bit? Help out?

41:15.223 --> 41:17.009
I'd like that.
You can start right here.

41:17.058 --> 41:20.016
All right. Cool. Hey, guys.

41:24.190 --> 41:25.225
(Traci) You're quiet.

41:25.274 --> 41:26.400
(Andy) I'm just tired, that's all.

41:26.442 --> 41:27.852
Right.

41:27.902 --> 41:30.939
